				<h3>Are there any keyboard hotkeys?</h3>
				<p class="margin-half">
					Yes! A letter or number in parenthesis next to a button means that you can use that key to activate it.<br />
					Furthermore, the following hotkeys exist:
				</p>
				<ul>
					<li><code>Ctrl + N</code> &mdash; Create a new race (when in the lobby).</li>
					<li><code>Ctrl + L</code> &mdash; Return to the lobby (when in a race).</li>
				</ul>

